g-muted text-foreground h-9 w-9\" aria-label=\"Toggle theme\"></button></div></div></header><main id=\"main\" class=\"min-h-[70vh]\"><div><section class=\"relative overflow-hidden border-b border-border\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_top,_var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-primary/15 via-transparent to-transparent\"></div><div class=\"container-af relative py-16 md:py-24\"><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-primary tracking-wide uppercase mb-3\">Interview mastery platform</p><h1 class=\"max-w-3xl text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight leading-[1.05]\">Master coding interviews with patterns, not random grinds.</h1><p class=\"mt-5 max-w-2xl text-lg text-muted-foreground\">AlgoForge is a free, SEO-first learning system: original explanations, multi-language solutions, Blind 75, Grind 169, company tracks, and roadmaps built for search and study.</p><div class=\"mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3\"><a class=\"inline-flex h-11 items-center rounded-lg bg-primary px-5 text-sm font-semibold text-primary-foreground hover:opacity-90\" href=\"/problems\">Browse problems</a><a class=\"inline-flex h-11 items-center rounded-lg border border-border bg-card px-5 text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-muted\" href=\"/blind-75\">Start Blind 75</a><a class=\"inline-flex h-11 items-center rounded-lg border border-border bg-card px-5 text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-muted\" href=\"/search\">Search</a></div><dl class=\"mt-12 grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-4 max-w-3xl\"><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/80 p-4\"><dt class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-wide\">Problems</dt><dd class=\"mt-1 text-2xl font-bold tabular-nums\">3987</dd></div><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/80 p-4\"><dt class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-wide\">Topics</dt><dd class=\"mt-1 text-2xl font-bold tabular-nums\">27</dd></div><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/80 p-4\"><dt class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-wide\">Patterns</dt><dd class=\"mt-1 text-2xl font-bold tabular-nums\">66</dd></div><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/80 p-4\"><dt class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-wide\">Landings</dt><dd class=\"mt-1 text-2xl font-bold tabular-nums\">199</dd></div></dl></div></section><section class=\"container-af py-14 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10\"><div><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight\">Featured problems</h2><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-4\">Jump into high-signal interview classics.</p><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li><a class=\"flex items-center justify-between gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card px-3 py-2.5 hover:border-primary/40\" href=\"/problems/two-sum\"><span class=\"font-medium\"><span class=\"text-muted-foreground tabular-nums mr-2\">#<!-- -->1</span>Two Sum</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide bg-easy/15 text-easy\">Easy</span></a></li><li><a class=\"flex items-center justify-between gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card px-3 py-2.5 hover:border-primary/40\" href=\"/problems/add-two-numbers\"><span class=\"font-medium\"><span class=\"text-muted-foreground tabular-nums mr-2\">#<!-- -->2</span>Add Two Numbers</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide bg-medium/15 text-medium\">Medium</span></a></li><li><a class=\"flex items-center justify-between gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card px-3 py-2.5 hover:border-primary/40\" href=\"/problems/longest-substring-without-repeating-characters\"><span class=\"font-medium\"><span class=\"text-muted-foreground tabular-nums mr-2\">#<!-- -->3</span>Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide bg-medium/15 text-medium\">Medium</span></a></li><li><a class=\"flex items-center justify-between gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card px-3 py-2.5 hover:border-primary/40\" href=\"/problems/median-of-two-sorted-arrays\"><span class=\"font-medium\"><span class=\"text-muted-foreground tabular-nums mr-2\">#<!-- -->4</span>Median of Two Sorted Arrays</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide bg-hard/15 text-hard\">Hard</span></a></li><li><a class=\"flex items-center justify-between gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card px-3 py-2.5 hover:border-primary/40\" href=\"/problems/longest-palindromic-substring\"><span class=\"font-medium\"><span class=\"text-muted-foreground tabular-nums mr-2\">#<!-- -->5</span>Longest Palindromic Substring</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide bg-medium/15 text-medium\">Medium</span></a></li><li><a class=\"flex items-center justify-between gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card px-3 py-2.5 hover:border-primary/40\" href=\"/problems/zigzag-conversion\"><span class=\"font-medium\"><span class=\"text-muted-foreground tabular-nums mr-2\">#<!-- -->6</span>ZigZag Conversion</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide bg-easy/15 text-easy\">Easy</span></a></li><li><a class=\"flex items-center justify-between gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card px-3 py-2.5 hover:border-primary/40\" href=\"/problems/reverse-integer\"><span class=\"font-medium\"><span class=\"text-muted-foreground tabular-nums mr-2\">#<!-- -->7</span>Reverse Integer</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide bg-easy/15 text-easy\">Easy</span></a></li><li><a class=\"flex items-center justify-between gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card px-3 py-2.5 hover:border-primary/40\" href=\"/problems/string-to-integer-atoi\"><span class=\"font-medium\"><span class=\"tex